Package: ggcharts
Type: Package
Title: Shorten the distance from data visualization idea to actual plot
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Thomas Neitmann
Maintainer: Thomas Neitmann <th.neitmann@gmail.com>
Description: This package intends to make it (much) easier to create common
    charts, such a bar charts, by taking care of a lot of data preprocessing
    and plot customization for you.
Depends:
    R (>= 2.10),
    ggplot2  
Imports:
    dplyr,
    magrittr,
    patchwork,
    rlang
Suggests: 
    tidyr,
    testthat (>= 2.1.0),
    vdiffr
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.0.2
